 -- Erik Damrose <damrose@univention.de>  Mon, 23 Jul 2018 17:37:18 +0200

univention-saml (5.0.4-23) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bug #47309: IdP configuration options regarding allowed LDAP attributes
    are now configured centrally in LDAP. This can be exended in the future
  * The default object DN for the configuration is
    id=default-saml-idp,cn=univention,LDAPBASE
  * A listener has been added, which replicates changes to this object on all
    SAML IDP servers
  * Previous UCRv values set to saml/idp/ldap/get_attributes are added to the
    default configuration on package update
  * Resync univention-saml-simplesamlphp-configuration when installing and
    upgrading package

 -- Erik Damrose <damrose@univention.de>  Fri, 13 Jul 2018 15:48:23 +0200

univention-saml (5.0.4-22) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bug #47309 Support raw simplesaml service provider configurations with
    replication

 -- Erik Damrose <damrose@univention.de>  Thu, 05 Jul 2018 13:15:59 +0200

